title: TABATA FINISHER // 5 Minute Spin Class • Intense Tabata Cycling Workout
description:
One round of spicy TABATA spin class! Add this HIIT session onto any cycling workout or conquer it on it's own! Here we go!

Who needs Peloton workout videos when you have YouTube!? Click LIKE and SUBSCRIBE to help support my channel! 
Thank you!

This finisher is from https://youtu.be/0_9Wo7ABQAU

Here is the full Tabata workout:
Warm-up: 30s
8 x 20s ON/10s OFF
Cool-down:  1 minute

I hope you enjoyed your workout! If you would like to donate to my channel, click here: https://donate.stripe.com/5kA6pl5Xr9Kp3WE6oo
Thank you so much for all of your support!!!!!
